title: We Test Tommy's Useless Trivia Skills
description:
Our Show Director, Tommy, is like a pop culture encyclopedia of knowledge. Throw ANYTHING at him - an actor, musician, movie, music venue, album - and he'll have a random piece of trivia or commentary on it that we bet you didn't know. We test him on the fly...
